name: Terry Ogburn
description: I can appreciate that an attraction on some level is important. I can be very appealing if you turn the lights down low, squint and imagine I am Terry. I’ve heard women say they would like their man to be like their bra – supportive. I think most men just want to be the bra. Luckily, I am not like most men who just want to get into your pants. I have no desire to cross dress. I’m serious about wanting to meet someone special. I’ll jump on Oprah’s couch when I do. If you would like to meet a guy with an IQ bigger than his shoe size, we should talk.
